    <j.0:event_part_of_dossier rdf:resource="http://publications.europa.eu/resource/pegase/157561"/>
    <j.0:comment xml:lang="en">The Commission was able to accept, as drafted or in spirit 15 out of 60 amendments and partly 10 out of the total of 60 amendments and was not able to accept 35 out of 60 amendments for several reasons: some of them were already reflected in the text, some could not be accepted for technical legal reasons, some of them referred to matters out of Community competence. </j.0:comment>
